attributes.review: I wanted to download president Donald Trump‘s app to finally see what him and his campaign is really about because he is often misunderstood. No you can imagine how caught off guard I was when the first thing they asked me for was my phone number I mean he has a wife and kids plus his 43 rape allegations but I could never imagine him cheating!!! After I put my phone number in I was bombarded with spam pictures and messages and it took hours to get off of my phone and eventually when it did come off of my phone I had to block the number and delete the app. Next thing I know for Secret Service men are knocking on my door telling me that I need to download the app again or they’re going to kill me and my family❤️. Overall do not download this app not only because the President of the United States is racist and homophobic but he can’t even manage to have a great app let alone manage the country.
